org.transitime.core.predAccuracy

Class PredAccuracyPrediction

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.transitime.core.predAccuracy.PredAccuracyPrediction

  • public class PredAccuracyPrediction
extends java.lang.Object
    For prediction accuracy analysis. For keeping a prediction in memory so that it can be compared to its corresponding arrival/departure to determine the accuracy of the prediction and store that info into the database.
    Author:
    SkiBu Smith
